OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F371A1775070658
OL,3,CFuneral of 8-year-old Amelia Kolpa
OL,4,Cgathers 1000s of bikers to escort the
OL,5,Ccortege
OL,7,FThousands of bikers from across the
OL,8,Fcountry have escorted a cortege for
OL,9,Fthe funeral of 8-year-old Amelia Kolpa.
OL,11,FAmelia, from Rowley Regis in the Black
OL,12,FCountry, had been receiving palliative
OL,13,Fcare for a stage four neuroblastoma
OL,14,Fand had been in and out of hospital
OL,15,Fsince the age of two-and-a-half.
OL,17,FShe went through just under two years
OL,18,Fof intensive treatment, including
OL,19,Fchemotherapy, immunotherapy and
OL,20,Fradiotherapy.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/6
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
