OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,372,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F371A1775070658
OL,3,CFuneral of 8-year-old Amelia Kolpa
OL,4,Cgathers 1000s of bikers to escort the
OL,5,Ccortege
OL,7,FHer wish for her birthday on March 3rd
OL,8,Fwas to receive 8,000 birthday cards,
OL,9,Fbut through the help of the community,
OL,10,Fshe ended up receiving more than
OL,11,F300,000 cards for the occasion,
OL,12,Fbreaking a UK record.
OL,14,FHer mum, Katarzyna Bartczak, announced
OL,15,FAmelia's death on social media,
OL,16,Fsaying: "Our dearest Amelia, you were
OL,17,Fand always will be our greatest
OL,18,Fmiracle. Our heart. Our light.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/6
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,372,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F371A1775070658
OL,3,CFuneral of 8-year-old Amelia Kolpa
OL,4,Cgathers 1000s of bikers to escort the
OL,5,Ccortege
OL,7,F"Thank you for every moment, every
OL,8,Fsmile, every glance... for the love
OL,9,Fyou taught us.
OL,11,F"This is not goodbye... It's 'see you
OL,12,Fagain'."
OL,14,FITV News Central also went along to
OL,15,Ffilm in February when a thousand
OL,16,Fmotorcyclists from a Black Country
OL,17,Fbiker group gathered outside her house
OL,18,Fto hand deliver the cards.
OL,26,@tD@HO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/6
