PN,37104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F371A1775070658
OL,3,CFuneral of 8-year-old Amelia Kolpa
OL,4,Cgathers 1000s of bikers to escort the
OL,5,Ccortege
OL,7,FAmelia's family also organised a group
OL,8,Fdance in March inside the Merry Hill
OL,9,Fshopping centre, in Dudley, which
OL,10,Finvolved members of the public coming
OL,11,Ftogether to do a mass Macarena.
OL,13,FHighfields Primary School issued a
OL,14,Fstatement which said Amelia was 'a
OL,15,Fspecial part' of the school community.
OL,17,FThe statement reads: "Throughout
OL,18,Feverything she faced, Amelia showed
OL,19,Fincredible strength and courage.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/6
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,372,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F371A1775070658
OL,3,CFuneral of 8-year-old Amelia Kolpa
OL,4,Cgathers 1000s of bikers to escort the
OL,5,Ccortege
OL,7,F"What so many of us will remember
OL,8,Fmost, however, is her beautiful smile.
OL,9,FIt was the kind of smile that brought
OL,10,Fwarmth and happiness to everyone
OL,11,Faround her.
OL,13,F"Her positivity, determination and
OL,14,Fgentle spirit touched the hearts of
OL,15,Fcountless staff and children across
OL,16,Fthe school."
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G5/6
